name: Visualgo
description: Visualgo is a platform that visualizes algorithms and data structures through interactive animations, helping users understand how they work in practice.

name: Flexbox Froggy
description: Flexbox Froggy is an interactive game that teaches the concepts of Flexbox, a CSS layout technique. Players help frogs settle into lily pads, applying Flexbox properties to solve challenges.

name: FreeCodeCamp
description: FreeCodeCamp offers a coding interview preparation course covering fundamental topics to help developers prepare for technical interviews.

name: Byte by Byte
description: This PDF contains 50 coding interview questions with detailed explanations and solutions to help developers prepare for technical interviews.

name: Memgraph
description: Memgraph offers a data structures cheat sheet, introducing essential concepts and implementations for developers.

name: Codility
description: Codility is a programming testing platform used to evaluate technical skills of developers. It offers challenges in multiple languages ​​and automatically evaluates submitted solutions.

name: Tech Interview Handbook
description: The Tech Interview Handbook offers free guides for tech job interviews, covering everything from algorithm questions to career advice and best practices for developers.

name: HackerRank
description: HackerRank is an online coding platform that offers coding challenges, competitions, and technical assessments. It is used by companies for recruiting and by developers to practice programming skills.

name: Kirupa
description: Kirupa is a website that offers tutorials and resources for learning programming and design, including tips on interviewing and web development.

name: Beecrowd
description: Beecrowd offers programming challenges and competitions so students can practice their skills. Students can also learn about new programming languages ​​and algorithms.

name: JS Challenger
description: JS Challenger is an online platform with JavaScript programming challenges. Offers hands-on exercises and instant feedback. Ideal for developers who want to improve their JavaScript skills.

name: Interview Warmup
description: This is a free online resource, developed by Google, that offers exercises and tips to help you prepare for a job interview in English more efficiently.

name: IME Algorithms
description: This site presents algorithms and their implementations in several languages, being a great reference for those who want to delve deeper into the study of algorithms.

name: Patterns.dev
description: Patterns.dev is a free online resource that provides design, rendering, and performance patterns for web application architecture. Helps developers build robust apps using pure JavaScript or modern frameworks.

name: GeeksforGeeks
description: GeeksforGeeks provides a complete guide to learning Data Structures and Algorithms from scratch with practical resources and examples.
